// `events` is intentionally empty: when built with the `bevy_ci_testing` feature, the
// testbed drives itself via `helpers::switch_scene_in_ci`, which pushes a per-scene
// `NamedScreenshot` event at runtime and exits after the full scene cycle.
// `fixed_frame_time` makes those captures frame-deterministic so Pixel Eagle diffs
// reflect rendering changes rather than wall-clock animation jitter.
(
    setup: (
        fixed_frame_time: Some(0.05),
    ),
    events: [
    ]
)
